           10 IND-PHONENO        PIC S9(4) USAGE COMP.
           10 IND-HIREDATE       PIC S9(4) USAGE COMP.
           10 IND-JOB            PIC S9(4) USAGE COMP.
           10 IND-EDLEVEL        PIC S9(4) USAGE COMP.
           10 IND-SEX            PIC S9(4) USAGE COMP.
